-------------------------------------
build instructions for the FFI module
-------------------------------------
./configure
make

-------------------------------------
usage in cadence:
-------------------------------------
make sure that libcadence_ffi.so and ffi.dasm are somewhere in your
CADENCE_PATH. you can now use:

%include "ffi.dasm"
@ffi pow 2 3

e.g. to compute 2 to the power of 3
